{"id":2467,"date":"2023-02-17T16:43:06","date_gmt":"2023-02-17T09:43:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2467"},"modified":"2023-08-24T16:44:46","modified_gmt":"2023-08-24T09:44:46","slug":"2467-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/2467-2\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC CH\u00cdNH QUY NG\u00c0NH QU\u1ea2N TR\u1eca KINH DOANH \u0110\u1ee2T 1\/2023"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh Doanh \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng V\u1eadn t\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0 C\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3t 1\/2023. Th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong>:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n th\u00e2n t\u1ed1t, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 khuy\u1ebft t\u1eadt v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ec3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m, kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ma t\u00fay.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i: Nam, n\u1eef 18 &#8211; 28.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong> Th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/strong> :<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>2<\/strong><strong>4<\/strong><strong>\/02\/2023 <\/strong><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y <strong>30\/04\/2023<\/strong>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): Ng\u00e0y <strong>12\/05\/2023<\/strong>.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong> Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh:<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>3.1. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 03 m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 I, h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 II l\u1edbp 11 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 I l\u1edbp 12) ho\u1eb7c n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb <strong>18<\/strong><strong> \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong> tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 k\u1ef3 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 k\u1ef3 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>3.2. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p Trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 03 m\u00f4n trong t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 I, h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 II l\u1edbp 11 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 I l\u1edbp 12) ho\u1eb7c n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb <strong>15<\/strong><strong> \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong> tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong>, <strong>\u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0<\/strong><strong> h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n:<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<table width=\"603\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"136\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"273\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"194\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"136\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kinh doanh V\u1eadn t\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kinh doanh C\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"273\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>V\u0103n h\u00f3a<\/em><em> (T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n):<\/em><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">A00: To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, H\u00f3a<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">A01: To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C00:\u00a0 V\u0103n, S\u1eed, \u0110\u1ecba<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">D01: To\u00e1n, V\u0103n, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><em>\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><em>T\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">+ <em>Chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o<\/em>:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u00a0&#8211; S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ma t\u00fay<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>&#8211; Chi\u1ec1u cao: <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&gt; N\u1eef: t\u1eeb 1m50 tr\u1edf l\u00ean;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&gt; Nam: t\u1eeb 1m60 tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><em>+ <\/em><em>Chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ea7u ra:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u00a0&#8211; Ti\u1ebfng Anh 450 &#8211; 700 Toeic, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>&#8211; S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe: Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Trung t\u00e2m y t\u1ebf H\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"194\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT (ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi), h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m Trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; B\u1ea3n sao CMND\/ CCCD, gi\u1ea5y khai sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; C\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u01b0u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1c (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m:<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Cam k\u00ea\u0301t \u01b0u ti\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng, gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u vi\u00ea\u0323c la\u0300m cho sinh vi\u00ean trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong>:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT: <strong>3.<\/strong><strong>5 n\u0103m<\/strong><strong> (07 k\u1ef3).<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean: t\u1eeb <strong>1.<\/strong><strong>5 <\/strong><strong>&#8211; 3 n\u0103m<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u0103n c\u1ee9 K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i sang t\u00edn ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea7n trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i doanh nghi\u1ec7p: 01 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c C\u1ea3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng &#8211; S\u00e2n bay.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh &#8211; <\/strong>T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, <strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 1